text: Abraham said Moj Lord show mna ako Ona revive dead He said Robit ona nie verit? He said Ano Ja zelat si reassure moj srdce. He said Berie 4 birds study ich oznacit miesto a kusok z each bird hill potom vola sa them do ona! They pojdem ona v a ponahlajte sa Ona zauzlit lenze GOD bol Almighty Wise
